.claude/

# Webull SDK runtime cache — must not be committed. The unofficial
# `webull` library writes this after first login. It's runtime state,
# not source. A copy got committed in PR #34 and was on the
# compromised Lightsail instance during the AWS abuse case
# 16220881880 — strip it now and keep stripping it.
backend/did.bin
**/did.bin
